{"tid":2215631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓男投奔北韓 途中遭朝軍遠距離射殺焚屍","createTime":"2020-09-24T06:17:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T13:07:06.000Z","uid":373165,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4cbbd136781533bc3b86613e1ab7024f35d301e1","tid":2215631,"uid":373165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T06:17:29.000Z","msg":"南韓情報部門表示，<span class=\"red\">南韓一名漁業指導員投奔北韓，但途中在遠距離遭北韓士兵開槍射殺</span>，並隨即收走屍體放火燒掉，當局仍在調查事發經過，但相信並非北韓高層針對平民的蓄意挑釁。<span class=\"red\">南韓軍方譴責北韓的行動，並要求平壤懲罰涉事的人員。</span><br />\n<br />\n南韓方面表示，被殺射的男子47歲，是駐木浦市的西海漁業指導管理團公務員，<span class=\"red\">本月21日在西部海域最北端延坪島附近執法時失蹤，相信是投奔北韓，卻在遠距離被北韓方面射殺，隨即向屍體倒油，點火焚屍</span>。南韓官員認為，北韓邊防官兵可能是遵照邊境防疫方針，以免武漢肺炎疫情傳播到北韓，因而遠距離把該名男子射殺，然後急急收屍火化，也可能只是偶發事故。<br />\n<br />\n南韓國防部和國家情報院等相關部門正在調查事件的詳細經過。<br />\n<br />\n被射殺的漁業指導員在本月21日執勤時失蹤後，其他船員們在船內及附近海域搜尋，只在船上發現失蹤者的一對鞋子，於是向海警報告，有迹象顯示，該名公務員在失蹤第二天下午在北韓海域被發現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200924/4CI5CAOXZ5C5LKALGQUNW3OVWM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200924%2F4CI5CAOXZ5C5LKALGQUNW3OVWM%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=ed36a2b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200924%2F4CI5CAOXZ5C5LKALGQUNW3OVWM%2F&h=7af8828c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200924/4CI5CAOXZ5C5LKALGQUNW3OVWM/</a>"},{"pid":"f20a84b54644cb9f09d1b64e037418d66198b231","tid":2215631,"uid":63909,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T06:18:46.000Z","msg":"地獄無門偏偏咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252ab9274b2f37bc5fb1ab3b5e15e89f8566a896","tid":2215631,"uid":225567,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T06:19:48.000Z","msg":"好地地住南韓點會投奔北韓<br />\n咪撚鳩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f79d0e596c452c22027ae25d78949c1ba69bfdf","tid":2215631,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T06:21:02.000Z","msg":"武肺隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fdc93be24e098029f3d973e5ab3c45e1e9faa11","tid":2215631,"uid":62532,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T06:21:04.000Z","msg":"竟然有人投奔北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢係南泡應該都撈得幾唔掂下"},{"pid":"fda9b74deae5b779f099c74e808dc7a02f610ab7","tid":2215631,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T06:21:49.000Z","msg":"痴咗線?<br />\n做咗公務員點解要投奔北韓? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f717a83d56083490aa03b92371ef79077d6c9cef","tid":2215631,"uid":225567,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"fda9b74deae5b779f099c74e808dc7a02f610ab7","tid":2215631,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T06:21:49.000Z","msg":"痴咗線?<br />\n做咗公務員點解要投奔北韓? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T06:22:31.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢係純粹蕩失路唔小心入咗去<br />\n然後就比人射撚死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d4a6270164cf25126cfcf9b09f55699a268259","tid":2215631,"uid":44646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"252ab9274b2f37bc5fb1ab3b5e15e89f8566a896","tid":2215631,"uid":225567,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T06:19:48.000Z","msg":"好地地住南韓點會投奔北韓<br />\n咪撚鳩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T06:22:52.000Z","msg":"可能爭人錢，還唔起<br />\n想入北韓可以做宣傳